race.description: Spartan Race Central Coast 21 Feb Provincial Hcp (C1)
race.comment: HEROIC DEED (11) got map favours on debut when a game winner in the six-horse field over 1150m at this track. Ashley Morgan retains the ride and finds a very average C1 from the sticky draw.  Sure to be thereabouts. HERMAN SAID (2) has his hoof on the till fourth-up with the blinkers going on. Gripped on late when a fighting second over 1250m at Taree in C1 grade. Tempo suits and will be strong late. ETOILE FILANTE (1) has found a bit of form in his last two runs and will appreciate the weight drop here. Strong through the line when third over 1250m at Taree. Goes well at this course and distance and he should get the right conditions. Each way. EGYPITIAN'S REWARD (8) deserves another chance after she covered ground in the run when a battling last over 1200m at Gosford. Will race closer from the low gate and must be kept safe in this easier race.
